---
import DemoLayout from '../../../layouts/DemoLayout.astro';
---

<DemoLayout
  title="SSL / TLS"
  description="Cloudflare's Advanced Certificate Management (ACM) solution provides robust SSL/TLS security with customizable options for cipher suites and certificate transparency monitoring."
  category="Application Security"
  labels={["SSL/TLS", "Certificates", "ACM"]}
  lastUpdated="April 2025"
>

  <!-- Overview Card -->
  <section class="card" aria-labelledby="overview-heading">
    <h2 id="overview-heading">Overview</h2>
    <p>
      <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/ssl/edge-certificates/advanced-certificate-manager/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
        Advanced Certificate Manager (ACM)
      </a>
      {' '}provides enhanced SSL/TLS certificate management with customizable options for certificate management,
      automatic renewals, and{' '}
      <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/ssl/edge-certificates/additional-options/cipher-suites/" target="_blank" rel="external noopener noreferrer">
        cipher suite
      </a>
      {' '}configurations. This is the recommended solution for managing SSL/TLS certificates on Cloudflare.
    </p>

    <h3 class="subsection-heading">Core SSL/TLS Features</h3>
    <ul class="feature-list">
      <li>
        <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/ssl/edge-certificates/custom-certificates/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
          <strong>Custom Certificates</strong>
        </a>
        {' '}- Upload and manage your own SSL certificates
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/ssl/edge-certificates/universal-ssl/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
          <strong>Universal SSL</strong>
        </a>
        {' '}- Free SSL certificates for all domains
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/ssl/edge-certificates/additional-options/minimum-tls/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
          <strong>Minimum TLS Version</strong>
        </a>
        {' '}- Control TLS version requirements
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/ssl/edge-certificates/additional-options/always-use-https/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
          <strong>Always Use HTTPS</strong>
        </a>
        {' '}- Recommended setting for secure connections and preventing HTTP plaintext
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/ssl/edge-certificates/additional-options/total-tls/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
          <strong>Total TLS</strong>
        </a>
        {' '}- Generally recommended for enhanced security
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="subsection-heading">Additional Resources</h3>
    <ul class="feature-list">
      <li>
        <a href="https://crt.sh/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
          <strong>Certificate Search</strong>
        </a>
        {' '}- Public certificate database and monitoring
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://certificate.transparency.dev/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
          <strong>Certificate Transparency</strong>
        </a>
        {' '}- Open framework for monitoring certificates
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://ct.cloudflare.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
          <strong>Cloudflare CT Logs</strong>
        </a>
        {' '}- Certificate Transparency (CT) log service, built on{' '}
        <a href="https://blog.cloudflare.com/azul-certificate-transparency-log/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
          Cloudflare Workers
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://pq.cloudflareresearch.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
          <strong>Post-Quantum Cryptography (PQC)</strong>
        </a>
        {' '}- Future-proof encryption. Visit the site to check if your Browser supports PQC, or view adoption
        trends on{' '}
        <a href="https://radar.cloudflare.com/adoption-and-usage#post-quantum-encryption-adoption" target="_blank" rel="external noopener noreferrer">
          Cloudflare Radar
        </a>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="subsection-heading">Cloudflare for SaaS</h3>
    <p>
      If you are a SaaS provider or platform, similar to{' '}
      <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/case-studies/shopify/" target="_blank" rel="extend noopener noreferrer">Shopify</a>
      {' '}or{' '}
      <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/case-studies/porsche-informatik/" target="_blank" rel="extend noopener noreferrer">Porsche Informatik</a>,
      then we recommend using{' '}
      <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/cloudflare-for-platforms/cloudflare-for-saas/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
        Cloudflare for SaaS
      </a>,
      which enables you to extend Cloudflare's security and performance features to your customers through custom
      hostnames or vanity domains. You can review individual usage through the{' '}
      <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/cloudflare-for-platforms/cloudflare-for-saas/hostname-analytics/" target="_blank" rel="external noopener noreferrer">
        Analytics
      </a>.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-1">
      Here is a{' '}
      <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/reference-architecture/static/example-cloudflare-saas-migration-plan.pdf" target="_blank" rel="external noopener noreferrer">
        high-level migration guide
      </a>
      {' '}to get started with Cloudflare for SaaS.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- SSL/TLS Video Demo -->
  <section aria-labelledby="settings-heading">
    <h2 id="settings-heading">SSL/TLS Edge Certificates Dashboard Settings</h2>
    <div class="video-container">
      <iframe
        src="https://customer-px4ru5rucxtgoo68.cloudflarestream.com/5801922ba9c1f3e80b64763afb4462cd/iframe?muted=true&preload=true&loop=true&autoplay=true&poster=https%3A%2F%2Fcustomer-px4ru5rucxtgoo68.cloudflarestream.com%2F5801922ba9c1f3e80b64763afb4462cd%2Fthumbnails%2Fthumbnail.jpg%3Ftime%3D%26height%3D600"
        loading="lazy"
        allow="accelerometer; gyroscope; autoplay; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture;"
        allowfullscreen
        title="SSL/TLS Edge Certificates Dashboard Settings"
      ></iframe>
    </div>
  </section>

</DemoLayout>

<style>
  /* ===== Section spacing ===== */
  section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  section > h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 3vw, 1.45rem);
    color: var(--secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
  }

  /* ===== Card ===== */
  .card {
    background-color: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .card h2 {
    border-bottom-color: var(--border);
  }

  .card p, section > p {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ===== Subsection headings ===== */
  .subsection-heading {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--secondary);
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0.75rem;
  }

  /* ===== Feature list ===== */
  .feature-list {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin: 0.75rem 0 1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ===== Utility ===== */
  .mt-1 { margin-top: 1rem; }

  /* ===== Video Container ===== */
  .video-container {
    position: relative;
    padding-top: 56.94%;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 2px solid var(--secondary);
  }

  .video-container iframe {
    border: none;
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    height: 100%;
    width: 100%;
  }
</style>
